es_train_then_validate_only()"]},{"path":"tests/test_multiple_testing.py","purpose":"Reality Check interface and bootstrap behavior tests.","public_interfaces":["test_white_reality_check_returns_adjusted_pvalue()","test_stationary_bootstrap_preserves_length()"]},{"path":"tests/test_overfitting.py","purpose":"PBO estimation tests.","public_interfaces":["test_estimate_pbo_bounds_between_zero_and_one()","test_compute_rank_stability_returns_correlation_like_value()"]},{"path":"tests/test_metrics.py","purpose":"Performance metrics and diagnostics tests.","public_interfaces":["test_compute_primary_metrics_contains_required_fields()","test_compute_diagnostics_reports_factor_exposure_placeholders()"]},{"path":"tests/test_stopping.py","purpose":"Stopping rules evaluation tests.","public_interfaces":["test_evaluate_stop_rules_stops_on_test_touch()","test_evaluate_stop_rules_stops_on_high_pbo()"]}],"dependencies":["python>=3.11","pydantic","pandas","numpy","scipy","statsmodels","typing-extensions","pytest"],"invariants":["All public functions are type-annotated.","Specifications and plans are immutable after validation.","No module performs file I/O except io.py and cli.py.","Backtest inputs are point-in-time and survivorship-bias-aware.","Walk-forward validation never trains on validation or test periods.","Final locked test set is evaluated exactly once per research cycle.","Every candidate evaluated in sweeps is recorded for multiple-testing control.","Transaction costs are applied before reporting net metrics.","Portfolio weights satisfy declared exposure and concentration constraints.","Randomized procedures accept explicit seeds for reproducibility.","Modules expose interfaces and skeletons only; no notebook-specific state or side effects."],"tests":[{"path":"tests/test_strategy_spec.py","scenario":"Load minimal valid strategy JSON and reject malformed constraints or missing required fields."},{"path":"tests/test_universe.py","scenario":"Verify market cap, price, liquidity, and security-type filters produce the expected eligible universe."},{"path":"tests/test_signal_mean_reversion.py","scenario":"Verify residual-return ranking creates long and short buckets and handles missing observations deterministically."},{"path":"tests/test_risk.py","scenario":"Verify volatility and beta estimators return aligned series and neutrality step reduces target exposures."},{"path":"tests/test_costs.py","scenario":"Verify commissions, slippage, borrow costs, and stress multipliers increase net trading cost as expected."},{"path":"tests/test_portfolio.py","scenario":"Verify sizing plus constraint enforcement caps name weights, sector exposure, gross exposure, and net exposure."},{"path":"tests/test_backtest_engine.py","scenario":"Verify overlapping 5-day tranches, daily rebalance schedule, and exit timing are implemented consistently."},{"path":"tests/test_walk_forward.py","scenario":"Verify rolling 5-year train and 1-year validation folds advance by one year without leakage."},{"path":"tests/test_multiple_testing.py","scenario":"Verify White-style Reality Check returns a family-wise adjusted p-value over the full candidate set."},{"path":"tests/test_overfitting.py","scenario":"Verify probability-of-overfitting estimation remains within [0,1] and worsens when in-sample rank diverges from out-of-sample rank."},{"path":"tests/test_metrics.py","scenario":"Verify primary metrics include net Sharpe, annualized return, max drawdown, and t-stat; diagnostics include turnover and factor exposures."},{"path":"tests/test_stopping.py","scenario":"Verify iteration stops after final test touch, excessive overfitting probability, or failed adjusted significance threshold."},{"path":"tests/test_cli.py","scenario":"Verify CLI skeleton accepts spec and plan paths, validates inputs, and returns nonzero exit code on invalid configuration."}]}
